From the brand

LIVE, LOVE, LE SPECS

Our story

How we got our start
Since 1979, Le Specs has become renowned globally for its iconic and innovative sunglass collections with a reputation as the ultimate summer accessory. Le Specs has developed an international cult following and become a true trendsetter in the global fashion market.
What makes our product unique
All Le Specs sunglasses are comprehensively tested to comply with strict international standards, and fitted with lenses that filter out 100% UVA / UVB / UVC and harmful blue light up to 400nm.
Why we love what we do
Le Specs prides itself on creating fashion-forward pieces, designed with quality, innovation and technology, whilst remaining affordable. With a focus on excellence and value, Le Specs sunglasses are created using exceptional manufacturing and technical expertise.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
